headline: J.B. Hunt Transport Services, Inc. Announces Participation in Upcoming Investor Conferences
summary: LOWELL, Ark., January 27, 2026--J.B. Hunt Transport Services, Inc.’s (NASDAQ: JBHT) Chief Financial Officer and Executive Vice President of Finance Brad Delco will host one-on-one investor meetings at the 4th Annual Evercore ISI Travel & Transport Conference in New York, New York on Tuesday, February 10, 2026.
